      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data (Hariharan et al.) documents all test conditions: flow rates 2.5–6.0 L/min (±0.05 L/min), rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM (±5 RPM), and 40% glycerol-water blood analog properties at 37±0.5°C. Condition documentation meets level 2 requirements."
