      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH values compared against experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. Maximum discrepancy 14.7% at 4 L/min / 3000 RPM; all other points within 10%. Mean absolute error 8.3%. The 20% acceptance threshold is satisfied for all operating conditions. A screening sensitivity evaluation of blood viscosity (±15%) confirmed that parametric uncertainty does not materially alter the pass/fail outcome."
