      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index is the primary regulatory acceptance criterion for CPB device submissions. Wall shear stress is the mechanistic driver of red blood cell damage in the power-law hemolysis model. Both QoIs are directly linked to the COU decision. Relevance criterion satisfied at level 2."
    },
