      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, selection of the k-omega SST turbulence model and power-law hemolysis model with documented literature support is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published benchmark studies for centrifugal blood pump flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al. coefficients) is the regulatory standard. Model form uncertainty not formally quantified at MRL 2; literature support documented in the simulation plan."
    },
    {
