    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The remaining 6 factors are appropriately scoped to level 1 per the MRL 2 assessment matrix and are satisfied through documentation and analyst qualification. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at worst-case operating point. Submission to regulatory body is supported.",
